{"tid":1770673,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"他們靠什麼強心？ - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-05T10:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:00:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4005b5c674b1cd0c74fbc5df4f51541fbee4af3","tid":1770673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191205/20818982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F20818982%2F&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=5585896d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F20818982%2F&h=5de9a746\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191205/20818982/</a><br />\n<br />\n他們靠什麼強心？ - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191205/large/1575440358_c9d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575440358_c9d8.jpg&h=83788b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月十四日，中共國家主席習近平在巴西出席金磚國家領袖會議，故意在國際場合恐嚇香港人說：「中央政府堅定支持香港行政長官鄭月娥領導香港，堅定支持香港警方執法，堅定支持香港司法機關懲治暴力罪犯。」香港黑警頭目鄧炳強謝恩說：「習主席的重要宣示，令香港警隊信心倍增。」<br />\n<br />\n而十一月四日，習近平在上海出席國際進口博覽會，也曾故意表明對香港民意之蔑視，召見港人公敵鄭月娥說：「中央對你十分信任，對你和其他管治官員的工作充分肯定。」香港偽政務司長張建宗也謝恩說：「習主席一頓話，不啻給香港政府打了強心針。」<br />\n<br />\n照道理，政府、警隊的權力與信心，應來自人民的支持與愛戴。但鄭月娥的偽政府及鄧炳強的黑警，卻只能靠習近平，以其一言為起死回生的「強心針」，因其一語而「信心倍增」。十一月二十四日香港區議會選舉，反偽政府、反黑警候選人奪得四百五十二席中的三百八十六席，這可作鄧炳強、張建宗謝恩詞的注腳。<br />\n<br />\n中共駐美國公使李克新十一月下旬在美中政策基金會晚宴上致辭，批評美國國務卿蓬佩奧的「與中共衝突，不等於與中國人民衝突」論。李克新說：「中國人民前進的步伐，與共產黨完全一致，不可或分。」也許，六四屠城之外，今日香港也是「中共與人民完全一致」的明證。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"95f97c16bf639725e292d01fe9b0470342665300","tid":1770673,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ee0a4d0cec0220c68adf15acb477a06498dfc54","tid":1770673,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">128  維園見</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NubQiBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNubQiBY.jpg&h=92e1c59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmZKn8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmZKn8j.jpg&h=63ee12ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqTnUd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqTnUd9.jpg&h=3e0f0960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ounWYCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FounWYCe.jpg&h=82df0bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KsKuy8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsKuy8t.jpg&h=252ad633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42rgYzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42rgYzb.jpg&h=833df8cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <div style=\"text-align: right;\"></div>"},{"pid":"ab2953b59d35c9f4c3f36547c687925608093e9c","tid":1770673,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"英國美國加